### 2. Lighting Fixture Placement üí°  
**Automate_Lighting_Fixture_Placement.py** | **Automate_Lighting_Fixture_Placement.dyn**  

Automate NEC 2023-compliant lighting placement with this Python/Dynamo script for Revit 2025, saving **6‚Äì10 hours per project**.  
This tool:
- Places fixtures in rooms using grid and boundary logic
- Supports **DIALux CSV** integration for lighting calcs
- Ensures **ceiling-hosted installations per NEC 410.36(A)**
- Avoids wall conflicts with precision placement
- Outputs detailed **CSV logs** for compliance review

üìÅ [Available here](https://github.com/DynMEP/DynMEP/tree/main/scripts)

- `.py`: For developers, paste into Python Script node  
- `.dyn`: Plug-and-play, open in Dynamo  

